Name: 3G Watchdog Pro.apk
Version : 1.5.2
Requires ANDROID: 1.6 and up
Category: Tools



Description
3G Watchdog Pro.
Guarding you against costly internet overages.
Pro version of 3G Watchdog mobile data counter / monitoring app, featuring:
* Advanced data usage prediction
* Billing rules (counts in blocks, ignores uploads)
* Usage history with graph &amp; CSV export
* Usage by application (Android 2.2+, unavailable on Dell Streak)
* 5 widget styles
* Backup/restore
* Redesigned UI
* Account/SIM with auto switch (requires a phone with a SIM)
* Import settings &amp; data from 3GW free (don't uninstall 3GW free before importing!)
* ... and more!
Translated in 5 languages (English, French, German, Portuguese, Spanish), more on the way.


